#: .strings.POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_NAME
msgctxt ".strings.POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_NAME"
msgid "Arsonist"
msgstr "Палій"

#: .strings.POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"The Arsonist is a close-ranged tank who uses fire as a means to an end. "
"Managing his Overheat meter allows him to deal high amounts of damage to "
"groups of enemies. Balance is crucial to victory.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Your attacks will be weaker when you're overheating. If you're in a "
"tight spot, Cleanse can immediately end the overheating period in exchange "
"for extending its cooldown duration.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Masochism's Anticipation stacks still build during the ability's "
"duration, meaning you can activate it early and exit with the max duration.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Cleanse can remove the fire debuff from your passive. Use it to get "
"out of a pinch."
msgstr ""

#: .strings.POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SUBTITLE
msgid "Manic Incendiary"
msgstr "Маніакальний палій"

#: .strings.POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_LORE
msgid ""
"A u d i o  r e c o r d i n g  t a k e n  f r o m  p e r s o n a l  r e c o r "
"d i n g  d e v i c e .\n"
"\n"
"P r i n t i n g  t r a n s c r i p t . . .\n"
"\n"
"Joining the UES proved to be easy. Especially with their job listings. \n"
"\n"
"A demolitions expert is not much different from the type of work that I "
"already do. And yes, arson is work. The military had been kind enough to "
"leave the old equipment of the Incendiary Unit lying around for keen eyes "
"like mine to find. It wasn’t difficult learning exactly what they were "
"trying to do with that unit, and it was a damned shame that they shut it "
"down.\n"
"\n"
"They were brilliant. They were brilliant, and the UES told them they were "
"psychopaths. I was only able to barely salvage the remnants of what little "
"hadn’t been completely destroyed. Even then, I haven’t gotten much of a "
"chance to test my restorations with the high security of my division.\n"
"\n"
"I heard from a colleague that there was a job happening. Some sort of rescue "
"mission aboard the UES Safe Travels to an uncharted planet. I’ve heard "
"stories of that place, not so nice ones about the creatures that live "
"there.\n"
"\n"
"Hm.\n"
"\n"
"Maybe I’ll go. Sounds like I’ll find some very good lab rats.\n"
"\n"
"E n d  o f  r e c o r d i n g .\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: .strings.POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_OUTRO_FLAVOR
msgid "..and so he left, with new bloodlust set ablaze."
msgstr "...і він пішов, у жару нової жаги крові."

#: .strings.POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_OUTRO_FAILURE
msgid "..and so he vanished, his only regret: a job left unfinished."
msgstr "...і він був стертий, єдине, про що він шкодує: робота не виконана."

